---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Contact
permalink: /contact/
pageDescription: "Contact Kumo Sushi & Ramen in Port Orchard — call for orders and tonight's wait, text the kitchen, or come find us on Village Lane."
---

<section class="contact-hero">
  <div class="section__inner">
    <h1 class="menu-hero__title"><span class="section__kanji" aria-hidden="true">連絡</span> Get in touch</h1>
    <p class="menu-hero__lede">
      It's a two-person kitchen — the fastest answer is always a phone call.
      Here's every way to reach us, and what each one is best for.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section__inner contact-body">
  <ul class="contact-grid">
    <li class="contact-card contact-card--primary">
      <p class="contact-card__kanji" aria-hidden="true">電話</p>
      <h2 class="contact-card__title">Call us</h2>
      <p class="contact-card__detail">Best for placing takeout orders, tonight's wait, and anything time-sensitive.</p>
      <a class="btn btn--ember" href="tel:{{ site.phone.tel }}" data-analytics="contact_call">{{ site.phone.display }}</a>
    </li>

    <li class="contact-card">
      <p class="contact-card__kanji" aria-hidden="true">文</p>
      <h2 class="contact-card__title">Text us</h2>
      <p class="contact-card__detail">{{ site.contact.smsNote }}</p>
      <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="sms:{{ site.contact.smsTel }}" data-analytics="contact_sms">Text {{ site.contact.smsDisplay }}</a>
    </li>

    {%- if site.contact.email %}
    <li class="contact-card">
      <p class="contact-card__kanji" aria-hidden="true">郵</p>
      <h2 class="contact-card__title">Email us</h2>
      <p class="contact-card__detail">For catering questions, feedback, and anything that can wait a day.</p>
      <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="mailto:{{ site.contact.email }}" data-analytics="contact_email">{{ site.contact.email }}</a>
    </li>
    {%- endif %}

    <li class="contact-card">
      <p class="contact-card__kanji" aria-hidden="true">道</p>
      <h2 class="contact-card__title">Come by</h2>
      <p class="contact-card__detail">
        {{ site.address.street }}<br>
        {{ site.address.city }}, {{ site.address.state }} {{ site.address.zip }}
      </p>
      <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="{{ site.address.mapsUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-analytics="map_open" data-location="contact">Directions →</a>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="contact-hours">
    <h2 class="visit__hours-title">Hours</h2>
    {% include "partials/hours.njk" %}
  </div>
</div>
